commit.message: Disable tests if ToxExt::Mock is unavailable

Initial review improvements

* Add maximum message size
* Improved style
* Updates for toxext v0.0.2

Remove obsolete comment

Comment indicates that the negotiation callback is called after issuing
a message to tie message ids to the multipart message extension. This is
a remenant of an old design that is no longer in use. There are no
message ids and we negotiate as normal
